    /// stay-at-`self.index_of()` anchor it pins at the boundary.
    ///
    /// Default body composes [`Self::saturating_prev`] with
    /// [`Self::index_of`] verbatim. The saturating-neighbor-index
    /// contract — the head arm returns `self.index_of()` for
