        // `Alpha`. Sibling posture to
        // `sorted_variants_returns_typed_variants_in_lexicographic_label_order`
        // on the (endpoint-anchor, sorted-listing) axis — both walk
        // `T::ALL` as their load-bearing primitive, one at the
